    <title>Hash</title>
    <link href="/2020/09/07/Hash/"/>
    <url>/2020/09/07/Hash/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<center><font size=6>字符串哈希（前缀哈希）</font></center><center><font size=3>written by ZhangZiheng</font></center><p><strong>题目描述：</strong><br>给定一个长度为n的字符串，再给定​m​个询问，每个询问包含四个整数$ l_1,r_1,l_2,r_2 $，请你判断$[l_1,r_1]$和$[l_2,r_2]$这两个区间所包含的字符串子串是否完全相同。<br>字符串中只包含大小写英文字母和数字。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>第一行包含整数n和m，表示字符串长度和询问次数。<br>第二行包含一个长度为n的字符串，字符串中只包含大小写英文字母和数字。<br>接下来m行，每行包含四个整数$l_1,r_1,l_2,r_2$，表示一次询问所涉及的两个区间。<br>注意，字符串的位置从1开始编号。</p><p><strong>输入格式：</strong><br>对于每个询问输出一个结果，如果两个字符串子串完全相同则输出“Yes”，否则输出“No”。<br>每个结果占一行。</p><p><strong>数据范围：</strong><br>$1\leq n \leq m \leq 10^5$</p><p><strong>样例：</strong></p><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-comment">// input</span><span class="hljs-number">8</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span>aabbaabb<span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span> <span class="hljs-number">5</span> <span class="hljs-number">7</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">3</span> <span class="hljs-number">6</span> <span class="hljs-number">8</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span> <span class="hljs-number">2</span><span class="hljs-comment">// output</span>YesNoYes</code></pre><p>哈希方法的核心在于“==映射==”。</p><ol><li>将字符串看成一个p进制数，即</li></ol><script type="math/tex; mode=display">hash[string] = \sum string[i]*p^{i}(mod\ Q)</script><p>例如abcd，可以将其看成$(1234)_{p}$，这样一来，字符串abcd可以表示成：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h[abcd]=1*p^{3}+2*p^{2}+3*p^{1}+4*p^{0}</script><ol><li>因为(1)式的值过大，所以可以将其模Q，映射为$0\sim Q-1$之间的值，即：</li></ol><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h[abcd]=(1*p^{3}+2*p^{2}+3*p^{1}+4*p^{0})\ mod\ Q</script><p>在(3)式中，根据经验值，$p=131$或$p=13331$时，哈希冲突的可能性最低；且$Q=2^{64}$。<br>此时$mod\ Q$的结果与<code>unsigned long long</code>自然溢出后结果相同。</p><ol><li>在需要多次询问的题目中，每次对字符串进行哈希会导致效率过低，因此可以预处理出哈希结果。</li></ol><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-comment">/*</span><span class="hljs-comment">h[]: hash结果</span><span class="hljs-comment">p[]: p[i]表示p的i次幂</span><span class="hljs-comment">str[]: 需要哈希的字符串</span><span class="hljs-comment"></span><span class="hljs-comment">const int P = 13331;</span><span class="hljs-comment">unsigned long long h[N], p[N];</span><span class="hljs-comment">*/</span><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)&#123;    p[i] = p[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * P;    h[i] = h[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * P + str[i];&#125;</code></pre><p>有了字符串哈希结果之后，我们就可以快速比较两个字符串是否相同。</p><ol><li>考虑如何得到字符串$[l, r]$之间的哈希值。<br>以字符串abcdef为例，要求hash(ef)的哈希值，此时$l$指向e，$r$指向f（abcd[ef]），有：</li></ol><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h(0\sim l-1)=a*p^{l-2}+b*p^{l-3}+c*p^{l-4}+d*p^{l-5}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h(0\sim r)=h(0\sim l-1)=a*p^{r-1}+b*p^{r-2}+c*p^{r-3}+d*p^{r-4}+e*p^{r-5}+f*p^{r-6}</script><p>注意到(4)式和(5)式前4项相差$p^{r-l+1}$，则：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">h(l\sim r)=h(0\sim r) - h(0\sim l-1)*p^{r-l+1}</script><p>这样一来，(6)式即为所求。</p><ol><li>当有多组询问时，只需考虑$hash(l_1, r1)$与$hash(l_2,r_2)$的值是否相等，即可判断两个子串是否相同。</li></ol><p>具体代码实现如下：时间复杂度$O(n)$</p><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">std</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">/*</span><span class="hljs-comment">h[]: hash结果</span><span class="hljs-comment">p[]: p[i]表示p的i次幂</span><span class="hljs-comment">str[]: 需要哈希的字符串</span><span class="hljs-comment">*/</span><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> N = <span class="hljs-number">1e5</span> + <span class="hljs-number">10</span>, P = <span class="hljs-number">13331</span>;<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n, m;<span class="hljs-keyword">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> h[N], p[N];<span class="hljs-keyword">char</span> str[N];<span class="hljs-comment">// 获取[l,r]的哈希值</span><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">unsigned</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">long</span> <span class="hljs-title">get</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> l, <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> r)</span></span><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> h[r] - h[l - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * p[r - l + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>];&#125;<span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;    <span class="hljs-built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; m &gt;&gt; (str + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);    p[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)    &#123;        p[i] = p[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * P;        h[i] = h[i - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] * P + str[i];    &#125;    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(m--)    &#123;        <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> l1, r1, l2, r2;        <span class="hljs-built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; l1 &gt;&gt; r1 &gt;&gt; l2 &gt;&gt; r2;        <span class="hljs-built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; (<span class="hljs-built_in">get</span>(l1, r1) == <span class="hljs-built_in">get</span>(l2, r2) ? <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Yes&quot;</span> : <span class="hljs-string">&quot;No&quot;</span>) &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-built_in">endl</span>;    &#125;    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;&#125;</code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
